  "title": "feat(router): support server environments",
  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nThis updates the `history` router to not rely on the `window` object, mainly to support server environments (required for SSR).\r\n\r\nThis is an in-between update before reworking the routing mechanism.\r\n\r\n## Changes\r\n\r\n- We guard around `window` access\r\n- One optional params: `getLocation`\r\n- The `history` router was not tested, I've covered the new code with tests\r\n\r\n## API\r\n\r\n### `getLocation`\r\n\r\n> `() ⇒ Location` | defaults to `() => window.location`\r\n\r\nReturns the location to store in the history.",
